{"title":"整容","authors":["易和元"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"整容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹麦皮特斯脱鲁普画  易和元  配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全凭一副刀和剪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改头换面不费难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫声变来它就变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本领高强赛神仙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听剪子呼呼响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头发一下都变短；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀子一挥快如风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一撮黑胡就不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥皂沫儿涂满头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易容药水喷几遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着镜子瞧一瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镜里现出新嘴脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"混世魔王希特勒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借尸还魂在人间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化身叫做阿登纳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死灰妄想要复燃！（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}